 Rana pipiens (1955) Evolution, 9, pp. 322-338; Ruibal, R., Thermal relations of five species of tropical lizards (1961) Evolution, 15, pp. 98-111; Schulte, J.A., Macey, J.R., Espinoza, R.E., Larson, A., Phylogenetic relationships in the iguanid lizard genus Liolaemus: multiple origins of viviparous reproduction and evidence for recurring Andean vicariance and dispersal (2000) Biol. J. Linn. Soc., 69, pp. 75-102","Bozinovic, F.; Center for Advanced Studies in Ecology and Biodiversity (CASEB), LINC-Global, Departamento de Ecología, Santiago, 6513677, Chile; email: fbozinovic@bio.puc.cl",,,,,,,,03064565,,JTBID,,"English","J. Therm. Biol.",Article,Scopus,2-s2.0-68649126528
